track_notes: This track to the summit starts at the village of Soleihas, it is a long walk and the last part is difficult because of the vegetation and no track available. There is two other ways to reach the summit, from La Garde and Solehas north! Take many water to drink in summertime
It is a nice 3 hours walk up to the summit from La Garde, in summer get some water and hat! beware of the sheep near the summit. plenty room for antenna and nice panorama.
